Description_lang: The Hour of Twilight falls upon Ultraxion's foes.  Enemies caught within the Twilight Realm take $103327s1 unresistable Shadow damage.  Enemies within the normal realm are instantly pulled back into the Twilight Realm.  If no enemies are hit by Hour of Twilight, the Aspects will take the full brunt of the attack, disrupting the shield protecting the Dragon Soul and heralding the end of all life on Azeroth.
